<item>
            <title>[LU-18831] Add llapi_layout_set_by_fd to set a custom layout on an open file descriptor of a file without striping</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18831</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The goal of this function is to take in a struct llapi_layout and a file descriptor then convert the layout into the struct lov_user_md, then store it into the trusted.lov xattr. This will allow copytools to add a custom layout on restore for example.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
